// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Route registration (config/Router.bx):
//
//   POST("/banking/chat",    "banking.chat")
//   POST("/banking/approve", "banking.approve")
//   POST("/banking/reject",  "banking.reject")
//
// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Front-end flow:
//
//   1. User submits a chat message → POST /banking/chat
//      Response 202 → show review UI with question.toolName + question.toolArgs
//
//   2. Reviewer clicks Approve      → POST /banking/approve  { threadId }
//      Reviewer clicks Approve+Edit → POST /banking/approve  { threadId, editedArgs: {...} }
//      Reviewer clicks Reject        → POST /banking/reject   { threadId, reason: "..." }
//
//   3. If the next response is 202 again, repeat step 2 for the next tool.
//      If the response is 200, display response.response to the user.
// ===========================================================================
